Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finished the loading,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,board on the ship in order and wait for the next instruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi, you are not elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain here and protect Kicha and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi-kun, thank you for your willing but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't talk to me, you idiot vigilante!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are sounds other than the sandstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies, they are right there!
