Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Start attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take their weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back, be quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I fo~und you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! Play together with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We picked this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it to defend yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go pick something again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK, Suo-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Skulax...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of mud...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Skulux and the ship of Lykos, and also the mud whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the same {\c&H232D3D&\3c&HFFFFFF&}smell{\3c&H232D3D&\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,both the minds of the people of the empire I saw on the ship of Lykos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world Neli showed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,have made me feeling nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, why should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro, take a prone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guards encountered some intruders in the underground passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They seems to be the residents of Fallaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They've come as we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their aim should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.84,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the younger sister of the general commander Orca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She is confirmed to be with the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that she is guiding them to {\i1}the Room of Nous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's capture her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,according to the order of the general commander Orca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We should kill them as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,including Orca's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu...But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the mud whale here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question, intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.15,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1144,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.15,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(874,1000)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the {\i1}Daímonas{\i0} of Fallaina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't work too hard, you'll exhaust out, Pony-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My lads of the vigilante group, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We can not live through unless we hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Then it would be too painful to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}However, I did not want to lose anyone from the mud whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can no longer call you {\i1}the destroyer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! More pursuers will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my misread,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the people on the mudwhale,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.50,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(770,1000)}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,have stronger thymia than the people of the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama! The central tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,has been drilled a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the enemies are entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief must stay in the safest place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the support of everybody's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm the support of minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's the time I should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The reinforcements will soon be here from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuji-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to hurt the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave, you demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hukuji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakuji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Su...o...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk! I will take you to the aid station now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... trying to... sink the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's... wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to see... your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even... the world... hates you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I... love... the mud whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you still talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that old guy is already helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna revenge that old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then draw your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for your insult to Hakuji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm loving it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are looking like the doll's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already tired of dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry more! Scream more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Every guy seems to be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me that is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the world that is out of joint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the time is out of joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as that boy is my boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,could you stop please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as annoying as an fly! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.92,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,1000)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.92,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,1000)}σκύλος
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Skulax the Nous is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:25.34,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(804,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the same the Fallaina, we can't use thymia over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has done it well and got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can finish our mission as we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni-kun and you guys should hold the entrance with thymia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to destroy the Nous with the guidance of Lykos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the stained glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I'd definitely prefer this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we penetrate into the room of Nous so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is even no sign of pursuers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokusa, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Urumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi, are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I tell you as I'm the only one made a boob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I forced you to take me here, it sucks if I become your passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You Idio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are injured, stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine, Ginshu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me {\i1}Miss Ginshu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave it empty here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow even an ant enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}There are merely a few things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I can write done in my records...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The worlds people saw at their ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The worlds reflected in their eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}pass them down...
